org.nerd4j.csv.field

Class CSVField<S,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.field.CSVField<S,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - type of the source field format.
    T - type of the target field format.

    public final class CSVField<S,T>
extends Object
    This class performs the process needed to manipulate a CSV field from its String form to its Object representation and vice versa.
